# pkg/database/mongo

MongoDB client builder for `{{ .Name }}`.

`New(ctx, cfg)` accepts a `config.MongoConfig` and returns a `*mongo.Client`. It pings on startup to fail fast on misconfiguration. Caller is responsible for calling `client.Disconnect(ctx)` on shutdown.

Connection values come from `config.yaml` (database name) and `.env` (URI with credentials).
